</div></div></div>
<p id=3D"mntl-sc-block_4-0" class=3D"comp mntl-sc-block beauty-sc-block-htm=
l mntl-sc-block-html"> While it's understandable why you may dread this tas=
k, Daniels suggests transforming it into a fun activity between you and you=
r partner to prevent it from becoming a stressful to-do. For example, she r=
ecommends crafting your seating chart on a Saturday morning with brunch. "P=
ut the names on index cards and start working on it like a puzzle," she say=
s. "Then sit with it for a day or two before it=E2=80=99s actually due. Onc=
e you make it final, [send] it to your planner."
</p>
<div id=3D"mntl-sc-block_5-0" class=3D"comp mntl-sc-block beauty-sc-block-a=
dslot mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block u-no-article-width-restriction"></div=
>
<p id=3D"mntl-sc-block_6-0" class=3D"comp mntl-sc-block beauty-sc-block-htm=
l mntl-sc-block-html"> Looking for some more expert-backed tips to make thi=
s task a little bit easier? Below, we've compiled nine to keep in mind. Rea=
