 be attending your nuptials, it's impossible to start assigning loved ones =
to tables. However, once you know who's coming, take time to group attendee=
s based on how you know them (think: family, college friends, neighbors, et=
c.) By doing so, you'll start to see which attendees it may make sense to s=
eat together. However, these aren't the only groupings that are important t=
o consider. <span class=3D"mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-sc-block-adslot-inline=
"></span>"People who have kids around the same age, people who <a class=3D"=
