ing-guest-advice-5223504" link-destination-recommendation=3D"true" data-com=
ponent=3D"link" data-source=3D"inlineLink" data-type=3D"internalLink" data-=
ordinal=3D"2">traveled to be at the wedding</a>=E2=80=94find the commonalit=
y within people so they can have things to talk about, again like putting t=
ogether the perfect puzzle," Daniels says.
</p>
