select your tables</a>. Typically, you can expect to have four different sh=
apes to choose from: round, rectangle, oval, or square. If you're hosting a=
 large affair, you may opt for rectangular tables, which can fit more guest=
s around them. However, if you want your loved ones to have more legroom, y=
ou may pick <a class=3D"recommendation-inline-link" href=3D"https://www.bri=
