<p id=3D"mntl-sc-block_46-0" class=3D"comp mntl-sc-block beauty-sc-block-ht=
ml mntl-sc-block-html"> On the big day, you'll want to ensure guests are ab=
le to locate their seats quickly and easily. To this end, arrange names in =
alphabetical order on your chart. And if you're placing everyone at one or =
two long tables, create a diagram with numbered seats, accompanied by an al=
phabetical list of guests=E2=80=99 names and seat numbers.
</p>
<div id=3D"mntl-sc-block_47-0" class=3D"comp mntl-sc-block beauty-sc-block-=
adslot mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block u-no-article-width-restriction"></di=
v>
<h3 id=3D"mntl-sc-block_48-0" class=3D"comp mntl-sc-block beauty-sc-block-s=
ubheading mntl-sc-block-subheading"> <span class=3D"mntl-sc-block-subheadin=
